snippet.title: OLD CATS & DOGS can be SUPER FUNNY TOO! - TRY NOT TO LAUGH
snippet.description:
Old cats and dogs can be super funny too! TRY NOT TO LAUGH! Just look how all these senior cats & dogs play, behave, react to kittens and puppies,... So ridiculous, funny and cute! What is your favorite clip? :) Hope you like our compilation, please share it and SUBSCRIBE! Watch also our other videos!
